{"tid":2281941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要求立法禁止肥婆喺感情台叫春","createTime":"2020-11-11T12:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T01:03:21.000Z","uid":366192,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9837fba63c100128b578fe298e1f64e2b8362d2","tid":2281941,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"每次見親啲肥婆開po就想像到佢地流晒口水覆人個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先食緊飯 睇到個肥婆開po差啲嘔咗出嚟<br />\n好心你地咪撚叫春啦 隔住個mon都聽到你地扁桃腺腫脹果把肥閪聲<br />\n屌你老母全部肥婆個係樣衰人賤性格閪 仲要肥撚到仆街<br />\n我代表藍波撚要求立法禁止肥婆喺感情台叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLunch哥見字可摸以幫我寫信比林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主好波:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樣衰唔係罪，係不幸。生得醜唔係你嘅責任，要怪嘅，只好怪上帝<br />\n但係，肥，就係你嘅錯！ 一個人好地地係唔會肥嘅，你變得做肥人，梗係食咗多過你需要嘅嘢啦 喺呢個仲有咁多人捱餓嘅時代，你竟然食咁多嘢？ 肥係貪心嘅表現，係唔公平嘅象徵 肥人臃腫畸形嘅身體，已經充分顯示出佢哋嘅唔道德<br />\n肥人係罪犯，佢哋甚至比小偷、殺人犯更無恥 一般犯人都會掩飾自己犯咗嘅罪 但係肥人，佢哋竟然將自己嘅罪證放晒響個身上，就好似一個殺人犯拖住條屍周街走咁 你話，見到肥人有乜辦法唔憤怒？<br />\n所以，見到肥人應該即刻鬧佢，就算唔鬧佢都要鄙視佢，我哋要透過侮辱嚟喚醒佢嘅良知 喺街見到肥人唔鬧佢，就好似搭地鐵見到痴漢非禮學生妹唔出聲一樣 作為一個有良知嘅人，我哋應該出聲，應該鼓起勇氣挺身而出鬧到佢哋狗血淋頭！"},{"pid":"9857804bf4cb62d52cdbd4940e6d45cc06a84a0b","tid":2281941,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a06fdda1ab6f3a67e6fb531210f5dfb6bf931ccc","tid":2281941,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9857804bf4cb62d52cdbd4940e6d45cc06a84a0b","tid":2281941,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"你係肥婆嘅話請即刻離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b30477684f1447ed9bd0ea568aea6786ab1a06","tid":2281941,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"小妹我都認同"},{"pid":"6695299d8bfd121f42f7ea9eaf5a59e8a7d1dbd7","tid":2281941,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"882d89dadfadcc6764a77b13b03389f5d4d3ed71","tid":2281941,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次見親啲肥婆開po就想像到佢地流晒口水覆人個樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf553f347d11bc2e8134b66f533009d0e0e93746","tid":2281941,"uid":291803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06fdda1ab6f3a67e6fb531210f5dfb6bf931ccc","tid":2281941,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9857804bf4cb62d52cdbd4940e6d45cc06a84a0b","tid":2281941,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"你係肥婆嘅話請即刻離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"肥婆真係好撚煩 成日問算唔算肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你想人話你唔肥咪問肥過你既人囉 <br />\n問我地做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一句講晒 肥就認啦"},{"pid":"367545bb6d7b94e1e8a96383ccd3fe22baf18662","tid":2281941,"uid":174339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"我地唔係肥 係有肉地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9135263d964f30d6d7e06b44e8ce9d9258f2bae7","tid":2281941,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"又關條白卡佬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ece3b4879be96895ebaa8f57f2cb5a6b6815e8","tid":2281941,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9135263d964f30d6d7e06b44e8ce9d9258f2bae7","tid":2281941,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"又關條白卡佬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:03:21.000Z","msg":"連登手捉嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}